Spec's for game history in userdata management:

user-api/game

POST user-api/game/add
Request: game-id, game-mode (singleplayer, remote), player, result, time, (unexpected events occured), detailed information, backend token
Response: Status code

GET user-api/game/history
Request: user-name, number of requested games, (index range maybe), auth token
Response: Status code, games

